# Faz 2: Signal Generation Pipeline — Detayli Implementation Plani

## Kod Okuma Sonuclari (Architect Analizi)

### ZATEN MEVCUT (Faz 1'den):
- `IIndicatorCalculator` + `IndicatorCalculator` — TAM IMPLEMENT (RSI, MACD, BB, ATR, VWAP, Stochastic, SMA, Parkinson)
- `IFairValueCalculator` interface — MEVCUT ama implementation YOK
- `ICandleBuffer` + `InMemoryCandleBuffer` — TAM IMPLEMENT
- `Signal` domain entity — TUM ALANLAR MEVCUT (FairValue, MarketPrice, Edge, KellyFraction, MuEstimate, SigmaEstimate, Regime, Indicators)
- `TechnicalIndicators.BullishCount()` / `BearishCount()` — MEVCUT, multi-confirmation icin kullanilacak
- `IIndicatorCalculator.CalculateParkinsonVolatility(candles, period)` — MEVCUT, regime detection icin kullanilacak
- `MarketDataWorker` — indicator hesapliyor ama signal uretmiyor, GUNCELLENECEK

### EKSIK (Faz 2 eklenecek):
- `ISignalGenerator` interface — YOK
- `IPositionSizer` interface — YOK
- `ITradeLogger` interface — YOK (stub olarak eklenecek)
- `FairValueCalculator` implementation — YOK
- `SignalGenerator` implementation — YOK
- `PositionSizer` implementation — YOK
- 3 yeni `Error` kodu — YOK
- MathNet.Numerics paketi — YOK

