## TASK 5: Infrastructure — PositionSizer

### YENİ DOSYA: `src/Traxon.CryptoTrader.Infrastructure/Calculators/PositionSizer.cs`

Namespace: `Traxon.CryptoTrader.Infrastructure.Calculators`
Usings: `Traxon.CryptoTrader.Application.Abstractions`

Class: `public sealed class PositionSizer : IPositionSizer`

Sabitler (private const):
```csharp
private const decimal MinEdge             = 0.03m;
private const decimal MaxPositionFraction = 0.05m; // max %5 bankroll
```

#### Method: `public PositionSizeResult Calculate(decimal fairValue, decimal marketPrice, decimal bankroll)`

Algoritma:
1. `var edge = Math.Abs(fairValue - marketPrice)`
2. `if (edge < MinEdge || bankroll <= 0m) return new PositionSizeResult(0m, 0m, edge, false)`
3. Kelly fraction hesapla:
   ```csharp
   // UP signal: f* = (fairValue - marketPrice) / (1 - marketPrice)
   // DOWN signal: f* = (marketPrice - fairValue) / marketPrice
   decimal kellyFull;
   if (fairValue > marketPrice)
       kellyFull = marketPrice > 0.9999m ? 0m : (fairValue - marketPrice) / (1m - marketPrice);
   else
       kellyFull = marketPrice < 0.0001m ? 0m : (marketPrice - fairValue) / marketPrice;
   ```
4. Half Kelly + max cap:
   ```csharp
   var halfKelly    = kellyFull / 2m;
   var maxPosition  = bankroll * MaxPositionFraction;
   var positionSize = Math.Min(halfKelly * bankroll, maxPosition);
   positionSize     = Math.Max(0m, positionSize);
   ```
5. `return new PositionSizeResult(Math.Round(halfKelly, 6), Math.Round(positionSize, 2), Math.Round(edge, 6), true)`

